{"tid":979001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：野狗野貓會被人道毀滅，野豬為何有不同待遇？","createTime":"2019-01-12T10:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T04:40:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":256,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"7019caee556deb8bf1da3cb7dc50171d29a8f4fc","tid":979001,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190112/s00001/90b954a3da7939a519ac87a8609e5d67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190112%2Fs00001%2F90b954a3da7939a519ac87a8609e5d67.jpg&h=128aa507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n漁護署周三（9日）回覆立法會議員提問，指去年首10個月接獲679宗野豬出沒及滋擾報告，當中5宗個案涉及野豬傷人。前特首梁振英今日在facebook發帖，稱其寓所附近每晚有野豬「摷開垃圾袋」覓食，引來野狗、野貓、老鼠及曱甴，質疑「野狗野貓會被人道毀滅，老鼠和曱甴會被毒殺，野豬為什麼有不同待遇？」<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在fb上載野豬翻找大型垃圾桶，及垃圾散落一地的照片。他指，野豬靠吃家庭垃圾維生，「沒有其他更好的食物來源」，其家附近每晚有野豬「摷開垃圾袋食頭圍，然後是野狗野貓，食尾圍的是老鼠和曱甴」。他認為只要沒有野豬，「垃圾站一帶不會一地廚餘，不會有這麼多的野狗野貓老鼠和曱甴」。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署前年開始暫停由民間狩獵隊狩獵野豬，自去年2月起推行野豬絕育計劃，截至去年12月共為54隻野豬施絕育手術，希望控制野豬數量。但梁振英認為，只為部分野豬避孕或絕育，「意味着未來幾年野豬數目不會減少，衛生問題還是沒有解決」。"},{"pid":"97c63a7b31a758513a6d23e44e158eeeebad1fc5","tid":979001,"uid":20933,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190112/s00001/90b8752801f2833d4064f649cf7c2e41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190112%2Fs00001%2F90b8752801f2833d4064f649cf7c2e41.jpg&h=91489cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英指其家附近每晩有野豬出沒。（梁振英fb圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190112/s00001/90b6547df24958f996982e1c9341be5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190112%2Fs00001%2F90b6547df24958f996982e1c9341be5a.jpg&h=3b943f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英指其家附近每晩有野豬在垃圾站和公共垃圾桶覓食。（梁振英fb圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190112/s00001/90b72a26c000a5eace2e496397af37f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190112%2Fs00001%2F90b72a26c000a5eace2e496397af37f2.jpg&h=1a7da670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英指野豬影響其家附近的衛生。（梁振英fb圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190112/s00001/1547290142821/%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC%E6%91%B7%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%A4%99%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E9%87%8E%E7%8B%97%E9%87%8E%E8%B2%93%E6%9C%83%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%AF%80%E6%BB%85-%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%BE%85%E9%81%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190112%2Fs00001%2F1547290142821%2F%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E6%2591%25B7%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E7%25A4%2599%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E9%2587%258E%25E7%258B%2597%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B2%2593%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AF%2580%25E6%25BB%2585-%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BE%2585%25E9%2581%2587&d=DLtGKLuzkPsemgmfAMyggQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=115fb53e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190112%2Fs00001%2F1547290142821%2F%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E6%2591%25B7%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E7%25A4%2599%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E9%2587%258E%25E7%258B%2597%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B2%2593%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AF%2580%25E6%25BB%2585-%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BE%2585%25E9%2581%2587&h=874203e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190112/s00001/154